00:48:44.020 --> 00:48:46.020
You need someone you can trust with your bowling ball.

00:48:46.020 --> 00:48:48.020
Give it to Pete.

00:48:48.020 --> 00:48:50.020
He deserves it.

00:48:50.020 --> 00:48:52.020
Paid for by the committee to compete the bowling ball.

00:48:52.020 --> 00:48:54.020
If I was going to win,

00:48:54.020 --> 00:48:57.020
I'd have to beat him at his own game.

