Answer. Older Pete.

00:49:31.520 --> 00:49:33.520
Bye-bye.

00:49:33.520 --> 00:49:35.520
Not good enough.

00:49:35.520 --> 00:49:37.520
She wasn't going to let our family fall apart

00:49:37.520 --> 00:49:39.520
