00:52:44.770 --> 00:52:49.100
Ball!

00:52:49.100 --> 00:52:51.100
Out with it, old man.

00:52:51.100 --> 00:52:53.100
You'll be sorry.

00:52:53.100 --> 00:53:01.220
Disrupt their families?

00:53:01.220 --> 00:53:03.220
Get her lover.

00:53:03.220 --> 00:53:09.090
Legless dog.

00:53:09.090 --> 00:53:11.090
This!

00:53:11.090 --> 00:53:31.200
The battle went on for hours.

00:53:31.200 --> 00:53:33.200
The ball was the fiercest

00:53:33.200 --> 00:53:35.200
foe Artie had ever tangled with.

00:53:37.200 --> 00:53:40.860
And in the end,

00:53:40.860 --> 00:53:42.860
the strong man went down.

00:53:42.860 --> 00:53:46.210
Foolish man.

00:53:46.210 --> 00:53:48.210
Brave.

00:53:48.210 --> 00:53:50.210
But foolish.

00:53:50.210 --> 00:54:00.370
With Artie defeated,

00:54:00.370 --> 00:54:02.370
nothing could stop us

00:54:02.370 --> 00:54:04.370
from the madness of the final showdown.

00:54:04.370 --> 00:54:06.370
Two Pete's

00:54:06.370 --> 00:54:08.370
would enter that room.

00:54:08.370 --> 00:54:10.370
Only one

00:54:10.370 --> 00:54:12.370
would come out.

00:54:12.370 --> 00:54:14.370
It's not too late to stop.

00:54:14.370 --> 00:54:16.370
Quit stalling, Chunderhead.

00:54:16.370 --> 00:54:18.370
Make me laugh.

00:54:18.370 --> 00:54:20.370
And so it began.

00:54:20.370 --> 00:54:22.370
At first,

00:54:22.370 --> 00:54:24.370
we just stood there, probing each other

00:54:24.370 --> 00:54:26.370
for weaknesses.

00:54:26.370 --> 00:54:30.290
Then suddenly,

00:54:30.290 --> 00:54:32.290
Pete attacked with a barrage

00:54:32.290 --> 00:54:34.290
of face twitches and tongue swirls

00:54:34.290 --> 00:54:36.290
that normally would have obliterated me.

00:54:36.290 --> 00:54:38.290
But I was ready.

00:54:38.290 --> 00:54:40.290
And came right back

00:54:40.290 --> 00:54:42.290
with the Wisconsin ear wiggle

00:54:42.290 --> 00:54:44.290
I picked up last summer in Sheboygan.

00:54:44.290 --> 00:54:46.290
I caught him off guard,

00:54:46.290 --> 00:54:48.290
but he didn't crack a smile.

00:54:48.290 --> 00:55:07.860
The battle was raging.

00:55:07.860 --> 00:55:09.860
Meanwhile,

00:55:09.860 --> 00:55:11.860
