00:55:11.860 --> 00:55:13.860
It started when Grandpa

00:55:13.860 --> 00:55:17.740
brought out cookies and milk.

00:55:17.740 --> 00:55:19.740
Maybe we should go up there.

00:55:19.740 --> 00:55:21.740
No. I forbid it.

00:55:21.740 --> 00:55:23.740
The ball must be passed on.

00:55:23.740 --> 00:55:25.740
Nothing can stop it.

00:55:25.740 --> 00:55:29.440
Drink that.

00:55:29.440 --> 00:55:36.140
It's milk.

00:55:36.140 --> 00:55:38.140
The contest slogged on

00:55:38.140 --> 00:55:40.140
for hour after brutal hour.

00:55:40.140 --> 00:55:42.140
The way it was going,

00:55:42.140 --> 00:55:44.140
maybe it would last the rest of our lives.

00:55:44.140 --> 00:55:46.140
It was insane.

00:55:46.140 --> 00:55:48.140
It was inhuman.

00:55:48.140 --> 00:55:50.140
Without warning,

00:55:50.140 --> 00:56:01.420
