00:56:01.420 --> 00:56:03.420
While we faced off against each other,

00:56:03.420 --> 00:56:05.420
Dad finally got up the nerve

00:56:05.420 --> 00:56:07.420
to face off against his dad.

00:56:07.420 --> 00:56:09.420
Who ate all the cookies?

00:56:09.420 --> 00:56:11.420
You know what sugar does to your teeth?

00:56:11.420 --> 00:56:13.420
Come on out with it. Who did it?

00:56:13.420 --> 00:56:15.420
You want to know who ate the cookies?

00:56:15.420 --> 00:56:17.420
You want to know? I'll tell you.

00:56:17.420 --> 00:56:19.420
I ate the cookies.

00:56:19.420 --> 00:56:21.420
And you want to know what else?

00:56:21.420 --> 00:56:23.420
I didn't finish my milk.

00:56:23.420 --> 00:56:25.420
What do you think of that?

00:56:25.420 --> 00:56:29.500
Spunky.

00:56:29.500 --> 00:56:31.500
My name is not spunky.

00:56:31.500 --> 00:56:34.780
My name is

00:56:34.780 --> 00:56:36.780
this is my house

00:56:36.780 --> 00:56:38.780
and my wife and my kids

00:56:38.780 --> 00:56:40.780
