00:56:40.780 --> 00:56:42.780
This war is over.

00:56:42.780 --> 00:56:44.780
But it wasn't.

00:56:44.780 --> 00:56:46.780
Me and Pete were locked in a death stare

00:56:46.780 --> 00:56:48.780
