00:56:48.780 --> 00:56:50.780
As the intensity increased,

00:56:50.780 --> 00:56:52.780
I started to hallucinate.

00:56:52.780 --> 00:57:04.860
And I know he was going

00:57:04.860 --> 00:57:06.860
