00:57:06.860 --> 00:57:08.860
Pete! Pete!

00:57:08.860 --> 00:57:10.860
Open the door!

00:57:10.860 --> 00:57:12.860
I didn't know how much longer we could take him.

00:57:12.860 --> 00:57:14.860
But then, something happened.

00:57:14.860 --> 00:57:16.860
I was able to see Pete again

00:57:16.860 --> 00:57:18.860
for what he really was.

00:57:18.860 --> 00:57:20.860
And I realized,

00:57:20.860 --> 00:57:22.860
after all those hours,

00:57:22.860 --> 00:57:24.860
I wasn't staring at my enemy.

00:57:24.860 --> 00:57:26.860
I was staring at my best friend.

00:57:26.860 --> 00:57:28.860
I guess Pete felt the same way.

00:57:28.860 --> 00:57:30.860
And finally,

00:57:30.860 --> 00:57:32.860
the sheer stupidity of what we were doing

00:57:32.860 --> 00:57:42.930
got to us.

00:57:42.930 --> 00:57:44.930
The battle for the ball

00:57:44.930 --> 00:57:48.620
was over.

00:57:48.620 --> 00:58:00.030
I, uh,

00:58:00.030 --> 00:58:02.030
I was wrong

00:58:02.030 --> 00:58:04.030
to interfere with your family.

00:58:04.030 --> 00:58:06.030
And it spunk

00:58:06.030 --> 00:58:08.030
um,

00:58:08.030 --> 00:58:10.030
