00:58:16.030 --> 00:58:18.030
Instead of good.

00:58:18.030 --> 00:58:21.730
Well, I don't know about that, dad.

00:58:21.730 --> 00:58:23.730
It did have the power

00:58:23.730 --> 00:58:25.730
to show you that your son

00:58:25.730 --> 00:58:27.730
had grown up.

00:58:27.730 --> 00:58:29.730
Maybe you'd like to stay around a while

00:58:29.730 --> 00:58:31.730
and get to know him.

00:58:31.730 --> 00:58:33.730
Huh?

00:58:33.730 --> 00:58:35.730
Soon after that,

00:58:35.730 --> 00:58:37.730
