00:58:47.730 --> 00:58:49.730
including drinking non-milk beverages.

00:58:49.730 --> 00:58:51.730
And as for rolling thunder,

00:58:51.730 --> 00:58:53.730
now that no one desired it anymore,

00:58:53.730 --> 00:58:55.730
it had lost most of its evil power.

00:58:55.730 --> 00:58:57.730
Even so,

00:58:57.730 --> 00:58:59.730
