00:58:59.730 --> 00:59:01.730
So after Grandpa taught Artie

00:59:01.730 --> 00:59:03.730
how to toss it with a sacred

00:59:03.730 --> 00:59:05.730
Tibetan power jam,

00:59:05.730 --> 00:59:07.730
it was time to say goodbye.

00:59:15.730 --> 00:59:21.380
We never knew where rolling

00:59:21.380 --> 00:59:23.380
thunder went,

00:59:23.380 --> 00:59:25.380
or if it would ever come back.

00:59:25.380 --> 00:59:27.380
But one thing was certain.

00:59:27.380 --> 00:59:29.380
We had learned our lesson.

00:59:29.380 --> 00:59:31.380
And next time,

00:59:31.380 --> 00:59:33.380
if it ever returned,

00:59:33.380 --> 01:00:30.260
