01:40:02.180 --> 01:40:03.180
Oh, is that right?

01:40:03.180 --> 01:40:04.420
Well, we'll just see about that.

01:40:04.420 --> 01:40:09.210
Michael, get down here right now.

01:40:09.210 --> 01:40:10.130
You know what?

01:40:10.130 --> 01:40:11.650
Why are you so late?

01:40:11.650 --> 01:40:13.490
And what's this I hear about you not caring what time

01:40:13.490 --> 01:40:15.090
