01:40:20.770 --> 01:40:21.890
You have to do your homework.

01:40:21.890 --> 01:40:23.170
You have to have a bath.

01:40:23.170 --> 01:40:24.530
We haven't even had dinner.

01:40:24.530 --> 01:40:25.930
I've been telling you this kind of thing

01:40:25.930 --> 01:40:29.770
since you were five years old.

01:40:29.770 --> 01:40:32.290
Now, listen, I have to be able to count on you.

01:40:32.290 --> 01:40:33.210
You're the man of the house.

01:40:33.210 --> 01:40:33.970
I want to go.

01:40:33.970 --> 01:40:36.250
Look at me, young man, when I talk to you.

01:40:36.250 --> 01:40:37.730
Now, I want you to get up in your room,

01:40:37.730 --> 01:40:39.330
and I don't want to hear one word out of you

01:40:39.330 --> 01:40:40.290
until dinner's on the table.

01:40:40.290 --> 01:41:17.840
Is that clear?

01:41:17.840 --> 01:41:20.980
Yeah.

01:41:20.980 --> 01:41:22.220
