01:41:22.220 --> 01:41:23.540
Wash up.

01:41:23.540 --> 01:41:29.020
OK.

01:41:29.020 --> 01:41:30.700
Are you OK?

01:41:30.700 --> 01:41:32.300
Sure, mom.

01:41:32.300 --> 01:41:34.780
Just met up, Mike, forgetting you so upset.

01:41:34.780 --> 01:41:35.900
Don't worry about it.

01:41:35.900 --> 01:41:54.690
Let's go.

01:41:54.690 --> 01:41:56.170
Very funny.

01:41:56.170 --> 01:41:57.090
